Creating private key cert:
$ openssl genrsa -des3 -out mycert.pem 2048 
	create passphrase.txt with just the passphrase in it
Creating private key:
$ openssl rsa -in mycert.pem -out rsa_privkey.pem -passin file:passphrase.txt
Creating public key: 
$ openssl rsa -in mycert.pem -pubout -out rsa_pubkey.pem -passin file:passphrase.txt